<!-- Instructions Interface -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid black;
            color: green;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 10px 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
        }  
        .contact {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid black;
            color: green;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 10px 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #3d6677
        }

        button:active {
            background-color: #74a6ad;
        }
    </style>
    <h1>Instructions</h1>
        <p>The goal is to guess the word in 6 tries or less.</p>
        <p>If the letter turns <span style="color:#3A8065">green</span> then the letter is right and in the right spot </p>
        <p>If the letter turns <span style="color:#e3c020">yellow</span> then the letter is right, but in the wrong spot</p>
        <p>If the letter turns <span style="color:#2e2e2d">grey</span> then the letter is not in the word</p>
        <p>Try to get the highest score!</p>   
        <a href="/"> 
            <button class = "instructions">
                Go Back
            </button>
        <a href="/contact">
            <button class = "contact">
                Contact Us
            </button>
        </a>
</html>  
